## ADR-019 Compliance Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Main Method
    participant E1 as CollectFromContext
    participant E2 as CollectFromPending
    participant E3 as ResolveCollected
    participant Dict as ConcurrentDictionaries
    
    M->>M: Initialize followersToResolve
    M->>E1: Call with dispatchId
    E1->>Dict: TryGetValue(dispatchId)
    Dict-->>E1: ctx with immutable Followers[]
    E1->>E1: Iterate snapshot (lock-free)
    E1->>M: Mutate followersToResolve
    
    M->>E2: Call with dispatchId
    E2->>Dict: ToArray() snapshot
    Dict-->>E2: Pending fills snapshot
    E2->>E2: Iterate snapshot (lock-free)
    E2->>M: Mutate followersToResolve
    
    M->>E3: Call with followersToResolve
    E3->>Dict: TryGetValue + TryRemove
    E3->>E3: Call SymmetryGuardTryResolveFollower
    E3->>M: Return (void)
    
    Note over M,Dict: All operations lock-free<br/>ADR-019 immutable semantics preserved
```

